# Changelog

## [0.1.0] - 2019-xx-xx

### Added
- New action: comment - comments the node, without regarding for the presence of the attributes array.
- New argument: -s / --signed-actions makes Gerdr leave a comment before / in place of any manipulated / removed node.

### Changed
- Validation for each element needing an action and valid actions are now handled by the Config class, as expected.
- Gerdr is now PSR-12 compliant.
- Release date for 0.1.0-alpha was wrong due to a typo.

## [0.1.0-alpha] - 2019-10-02

### Added

- Remove elements and/or attributes with the "remove" action.
